name: Looking At You Through The Glass
description:
I love how your cheeks turn reds every time you smile. Loving your beautiful eyes, staring deeply to mine. It's like I can have the world for myself right now.

But something strange caught me. It's like there's something missing. And I realized that I can't feel the touch of your skin or smells your scent. All I can feel is just the coldness of this window. Because I'm outside, afraid to come in.
